	   <tr><td colspan=2>And I made one error that I can see off hand.&nbsp;&nbsp;I must have the word spirit stuck in my brain when I wrote it cause I said the grimy lance dropped off of a Lizard Spiritualist.  Actually, it drops off of the Lizard Ritualist... same spawn location as described.  1-3 hour spawn on him.<br><br>For all you SK out there that wanna go check on him, mem sense the dead and cast it when you enter the zone.  His pet will come up on track.  He harm touched me for 341dmg when i killed him one time, and 321 another.  I'm guessing he can range from 31-35.<br><br>Klissar Silverspine &lt;Call Of Ascension&gt;<br>The Nameless<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
